(550, 'Labyrinth of Nightmare', 'LON-066', 'images/LON/LON-066.jpg', 'Soul of Purity and Light', 'Common', 'This card can only be Special Summoned by removing 2 LIGHT monsters in your Graveyard from play. As long as this card remains face-up on the field, decrease the ATK of all monsters on your opponent''s side of the field by 300 points during his/her Battle Phase.', 6, 'Fairy', 'Light', 2000, 1800, 'Monster', 'Effect', NULL, '', '', '', NULL, '77527210', '', '', NULL, ''),
